<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="joining-elements" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Joining Elements</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>To join two elements of the same type going in a row, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Place the cursor between the two elements.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Join the elements.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>Do one of the following:</p>
        </info>
        <choices>
          <choice>
            <p>Choose <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Element</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Join Elements</uicontrol>
              </menucascade>.</p>
          </choice>
          <choice>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Join Elements</uicontrol> button <image href="join-elements-button.png" align="center" placement="inline"/> on the toolbar.</p>
          </choice>
        </choices>
      </step>
    </steps>
    <example>
      <title>Example. Joining elements.</title>
      <p>Suppose we have inserted two <codeph>itemizedlist</codeph>s.</p>
      <p>Let&apos;s join the two <codeph>itemizedlist</codeph> elements:<ol>
          <li>
            <p>Place the cursor between the two <codeph>itemizedlist</codeph>s.</p>
            <fig frame="all">
              <title>The cursor is between the two <codeph>itemizedlist</codeph>s.</title>
              <image href="list-to-join.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
            </fig>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Choose <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Element</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Join Elements</uicontrol>
              </menucascade>.</p>
            <fig frame="all">
              <title>The <codeph>itemizedlist</codeph>s have been joined.</title>
              <image href="joined-list.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
            </fig>
          </li>
        </ol></p>
    </example>
  </taskbody>
</task>
